&lt;p&gt;Indulge in perfect comfort at the end of your workday. Savor a bird&rsquo;s eye view of the city and the irresistible repose of a harmonious interior in Yasmin style.&nbsp;Yasmin&rsquo;s harmony of nature and style sweeps through the whole hotel which was opened on 23rd of March 2009.&nbsp;Hotel Yasmin **** welcomes you with golden exterior mosaics, with the freshness of a fountain in a ring of paving stones and mossy walls immediately at the entrance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Refined taste meets high functionality, modern interior with elegant use of space makes part of exclusive rooms and suites in the Hotel Yasmin ****. Conference spaces for 300 guests and gourmet restaurant with a sunny summer terrace are also perfectly equipped.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;166 comfortable rooms with modern amenities; comfortable beds, original designer furniture, and stylish, roomy bathrooms are our guarantee of exceptional comfort. Spend an enjoyable evening with an exquisite meal and wine in our restaurant, or on the summer terrace, or spoil yourself with our first-class room service.&lt;/p&gt;
